Global coordination is the ability for states to coordinate on a global level on aspects such as policies and international law enforcement.

It is generally beneficial for states to coordinate on problems that affect or could affect all of them such as [existential risk]().^[[Solving Global Coordination Problems - Anders Sandberg
](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=91FKgBURAV0)]

